headline: Elon Musk's remarks at the Milken Conference: Top takeaways
summary: Tesla (TSLA) CEO Elon Musk spoke at the 27th Annual Milken Conference about a wide range of topics, except the company's recent layoffs and robotaxi plans. Yahoo Finance Reporter Yasmin Khorram joins The Morning Brief from the Annual Milken Global Institute Conference to break down the top takeaways from Musk's comments. For more expert insight and the latest market action, click here to watch this full episode of Morning Brief. This post was written by Nicholas Jacobino
